{"tid":712802,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"屌打太妍善美 IU被業界評為“最佳Solo女歌手”","createTime":"2018-06-22T11:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T13:56:01.000Z","uid":34643,"like":31,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f9df564a7516b37c3a6a05769ca3da17e06c2246","tid":712802,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:28:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">壓倒性的優勢 三個加起來也打不過</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://file.mk.co.kr/meet/neds/2018/01/image_readbot_2018_1607_15148440673155084.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffile.mk.co.kr%2Fmeet%2Fneds%2F2018%2F01%2Fimage_readbot_2018_1607_15148440673155084.jpg&h=ea258f39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n體育首爾創刊33周年調查&ldquo;歌謠界影響力人物&rdquo;，IU以85分在&ldquo;最佳Solo女歌手&rdquo;中列第一，第二名得分33分，呈巨大優勢。<br />\n<br />\n這是IU繼上年在這個調查中取得第一後的蟬聯。2008年以solo歌手出道的IU不僅作為原創歌手，更作為制作人宣示了音樂上的成長，並獲得大眾的喜愛。美國紐約時報今年三月在&ldquo;25首歌告訴你音樂走向何方&rdquo;特輯中也介紹了IU。<br />\n<br />\n該調查是以35個企劃社的代表或理事級以上的1名高管為對像，選出每個類別的1-3位，1-3位各得3、2、1分而算出。總分為210分，一人能得到的最高分為105分。參加調查的企劃社高管名單包括：YG代表楊民碩、JYP代表鄭玉、SM金靜雅、Bighit崔裕貞、Woori李英俊、MBK樸圭賢、FNC社長趙成完、YMC趙佑明等35家較知名企劃社高管。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2018/06/22/720a7bee57be9aec450b59d752a9902e1529633253.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F720a7bee57be9aec450b59d752a9902e1529633253.jpg&h=59df48f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4171b09d0e7d76be68c0ab9eca1eda5a1d458729","tid":712802,"uid":8727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abba25500cb61cb0ae7734529faef064faf1ed5","tid":712802,"uid":46332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73470480c8664f3b3fe3f9d52a1cf28f9f8acfd","tid":712802,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"